description:
Welcome Devaun to her first Hogtied appearance. What a debut it was! We subjected this first timer to one of our hardest, most brutal formats Hogtied has to offer: the live format.

No cuts, no breaks, all on screen tying and untying. You see it all - unedited, real BDSM action as it happened. All the joy and all the agony. The safe words, the pain, the massive orgasm, and the beauty of pure spontaneity. Hang on for a fast paced trip into one of Hogtied’s most successful shoots; Real Time Hogtied at its best.
title: Devaun in her first Hogtied shoot suffers though a real time, no cuts, no breaks, brutal update.
